e a lot during my early days with England.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThierry Henry<br />\n&ldquo;It was a disgrace he didn&rsquo;t win European Footballer of the Year after Istanbul in 2005 and, for me, he will be regarded as one of the greatest midfielders of all time when he finishes.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nZinedine Zidane<br />\n&ldquo;There was a point when Gerrard was the best midfield player in the world. It is unusual to get complete midfield players who can do everything, but that is what he was.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSir Alex Ferguson<br />\n&quot;If you were looking for the player you would replace Keane with, it would be Gerrard, without question. He has become the most influential player in England, bar none. More than Vieira. Not that Vieira lacks anything, but I think that Gerrard does more for his team than Vieira does, and has way more to his game. &quot;<br />\n<br />\n弱智就唔好走出黎鳩UP啦好嘛  跣腳同無英超係柒  但係點會唔係英格蘭其中一個最勁既中場呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046bbb6dbd22355f18b984140f1d159f1a26bbf8","tid":1085201,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4edd606f383c198490f6c98e8162bf3f33075d88","tid":1085201,"uid":174940,"like":38,"dislike":6,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"6a6817d20af47ef385f897dd91359f2141541b9d","tid":1085201,"uid":127454,"like":7,"dislike":23,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T04:36:54.000Z","msg":"話佢最廢就聽過姐 邊個話佢最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZZxTaSwSxTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZZxTaSwSxTs&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP9wbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=b58d7428\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZZxTaSwSxTs</a><br />\n<br />\nWayne Rooney<br />\nQuestion: The best player you have played with England.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;d have to say Stevie [was the best England tea